# How to Download CMIP6 Data

1. **Install AWS CLI**  
   Download the installer from: [https://awscli.amazonaws.com/AWSCLIV2.msi](https://awscli.amazonaws.com/AWSCLIV2.msi)  
   After installation, open a Command Prompt (cmd) and run `aws --version` to verify the installation.

2. **Edit the Batch File**  
   - Remove any model/SSP paths you donâ€™t need.  
   - Update `BASE_PATH` to the local folder where you want to store the downloaded data.

3. **Run the Batch File**  
   Double-click the `.bat` file or run it in the Command Prompt.  
   Files will be downloaded automatically into your specified folder.
